Synopsis

One of the most versatile composer hindi Film Industry had ever seen, RD Burman brought about a revolution in the popular music of its time in the late 60's onwards, almost single handedly. For the next two decades, he captured the musical imagination of an entire subcontinent like none before --- right from the entertainment seeking popular masses to the connoisseurs of classical Hindustani music Western, Jazz, Opera and Pop music. And almost a decade and half after his demise, he continues to be re-mixed and imitated endlessely



